ABANDON

Usage:  abandon [target/coordinates] [confirm]

This command allows you to abandon a building or acre of land which your 
empire no longer wants. This falls under the cede privilege. Buildings and rare
crops require you to type 'confirm' when you try to abandon them remotely.

It can also be used to abandon vehicles.

